{"article_id":"ITZkxP3ZoJE7TRiM","edus":[{"id":0,"text":"Donald Trump managed to get \" This is McCarthyism \" and \" This is Nixon/Watergate \" into the same string of tweets","depth":5},{"id":1,"text":"as he reportedly \" just found out \"","depth":6},{"id":2,"text":"that \" bad","depth":7},{"id":3,"text":"( or sick ) \" President Obama had tapped his phones prior to the election .","depth":7},{"id":4,"text":"Trump poured out his claims in a series of tweets","depth":5},{"id":5,"text":"that sought to leap the already high bar of insanity","depth":6},{"id":6,"text":"set by his usual statements .","depth":6},{"id":7,"text":"Terrible !","depth":4},{"id":8,"text":"Just found out","depth":9},{"id":9,"text":"that Obama had my `` wires tapped '' in Trump Tower just before the victory .","depth":9},{"id":10,"text":"Nothing found .","depth":8},{"id":11,"text":"This is McCarthyism !","depth":7},{"id":12,"text":"Is it legal for a sitting President to be `` wire tapping '' a race for president prior to an election ?","depth":8},{"id":13,"text":"Turned down by court earlier .","depth":8},{"id":14,"text":"A NEW LOW !","depth":8},{"id":15,"text":"How low has President Obama gone","depth":9},{"id":16,"text":"to tapp my phones during the very sacred election process .","depth":9},{"id":17,"text":"This is Nixon/Watergate .","depth":6},{"id":18,"text":"Bad ( or sick )","depth":7},{"id":19,"text":"guy !","depth":7},{"id":20,"text":"An hour after spewing off these tweets","depth":5},{"id":21,"text":"- and mixing in the shocking news","depth":6},{"id":22,"text":"that the Russian ambassador had visited the White House during the Obama administration -","depth":6},{"id":23,"text":"Trump has provided no details of this \" wire tapping . \"","depth":4},{"id":24,"text":"But","depth":5},{"id":25,"text":"considering","depth":7},{"id":26,"text":"that it ' s Donald Trump ,","depth":7},{"id":27,"text":"there ' s a good chance","depth":7},{"id":28,"text":"that \" just found out \" doesn ' t mean","depth":8},{"id":29,"text":"it was part of a briefing from the intelligence community .","depth":8},{"id":30,"text":"Trump doesn ' t trust those .","depth":6},{"id":31,"text":"Instead , he may well have been sitting at Mar-a-lago in his jam jams ,","depth":7},{"id":32,"text":"reading his favorite source .","depth":7},{"id":33,"text":"He could be referencing to a Breitbart article","depth":8},{"id":34,"text":"posted Friday","depth":8},{"id":35,"text":"that claimed","depth":8},{"id":36,"text":"the Obama administration made two Foreign Intelligence Surveillance Court","depth":11},{"id":37,"text":"( FISA )","depth":11},{"id":38,"text":"requests in 2016","depth":10},{"id":39,"text":"to monitor Trump communications and a computer server in Trump Tower","depth":10},{"id":40,"text":"focusing on possible links with Russian banks .","depth":10},{"id":41,"text":"According to Breitbart ,","depth":7},{"id":42,"text":"those communications revealed no wrongdoing ,","depth":8},{"id":43,"text":"which is as trustworthy as any other Breitbart article .","depth":8},{"id":44,"text":"What ' s extremely clear is that Trump is trying to get in front of something","depth":2},{"id":45,"text":"and blow smoke at the way","depth":4},{"id":46,"text":"the evidence was collected","depth":4},{"id":47,"text":"before the rest of the story tumbles out .","depth":3}],"relations":[{"parent":95,"left":91,"right":94,"relation":"evaluation","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":91,"left":67,"right":90,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":67,"left":54,"right":66,"relation":"evaluation","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":54,"left":51,"right":53,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":51,"left":0,"right":50,"relation":"context","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":50,"left":1,"right":49,"relation":"attribution","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":49,"left":2,"right":3,"relation":"adversative","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":53,"left":4,"right":52,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":52,"left":